<s> A few notes on mailing to this list Hello all To simplify readability and categorizing, I propose that we stick to the following conventions:  </s>
<s> Use [xxx] in your email's subject line to describe the content and topic of the mail.  </s>
<s> For example, an email dealing with process issues, should be written [DOM TS Process: particular issue]  </s>
<s> Possible values are then [DOM TS Process] [DOM TS Design] [DOM TS Scope] [DOM TS Documentation] [DOM TS General] within which you can give the particular before closing and separate it with a ':'.  </s>
